name: Maka
description:
Hi everyone, this is my 3rd content creation.

This time I started to "play" a little with the training values, to try to get a good result with a not very extensive dataset and shortest possible time.

The next creations will be based on these training times, if the next tests go well for me, then I will share the values of the method (once perfected).

As always, all comments and criticisms are welcome, as they help me to continue learning.

Please, if you download the model, share the results ♥


Info: just 100-step TI trained on a dataset of 19 images
